{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_09_01",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 1話 想いに応えたい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストがBIG4になってしばらく経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After a while‚ Moon Tempest became one of the BIG4",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん\n今日の収録は長丁場でしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your hard work‚ {user}-san\nWe had long recording schedules today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 8.7666658718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。しかし三本録りの予定が\n急遽一本増えるとは思わなかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job. We were only scheduled to record three songs‚ but\nI didn't expect an extra one to be added suddenly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1999993007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "疲れているところ悪いんだが、帰る前に\n明日の予定をもう一度確認しておこうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to bother you when you're tired‚ but before we go home‚\nlet's check tomorrow's schedule one more time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.033332634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 21.0666658718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "午前中にライブの打ち合わせ、午後にラジオ収録と\nインタビュー、それから特番のゲスト出演ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A live meeting in the morning‚ radio recording and an interview\nin the afternoon‚ and then a guest appearance on the special program‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "今までもそれなりに忙しくさせてもらってると思って\nましたけど……BIG4になった影響は大きいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought we'd been already busy up until now‚ but\nbecoming a BIG4 has had a big impact.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.233332634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 39.2666658718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "朝から分刻みのスケジュールだけど、大丈夫か？\nさすがに休む時間が少な過ぎるよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a minute-by-minute schedule from morning‚ are you okay?\nYou really don't have enough time to rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 46.1666658718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。仕事を受けるかどうかは毎回確認を\nとってくれてるじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay. You always confirm whether you accept or decline a job\nbefore you take it‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6199106369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 53.0666658718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、サニピがBIG4になった時の目の回るような\n忙しさを目の前で見てましたから。想定内です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ I saw firsthand how hectic things were for Sunny Peace\nwhen they became BIG4. It's within expectations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "頼もしいな。確かにあの時期のサニピは\n忙しさに慣れてないこともあって大変だったからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're dependable. It’s true that back then‚\nSunny Peace struggled because they weren't used to being so busy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.0999993007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 69.9666658718
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "五人とも毎朝バタバタ準備をしてましたよ\nいつの間にかみんな慣れてましたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All five of them were always rushing to get ready every morning.\nBut before I knew it‚ they had all gotten used to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.1666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 77.5999992052
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃は「さくら達はこんなに沢山の人に\n必要とされてるんだな」って羨ましく思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ I felt envious‚ thinking‚\n\"Sakura and the others are needed by so many people.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0999993007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 85.8333325385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今は私達も……これまで以上に\n必要としてもらえている。それが嬉しくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now‚ we too… are needed more\nthan before. That makes me happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.233332634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "それに以前から応援してくれているファンのみなさんは\n月ストのBIG4入りを心から喜んでくれてるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ the fans who have been supporting us from the beginning\nare truly happy about Moon Tempest joining the BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.940378213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 103.1333371161
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "これまでの道のりを考えると\n辛い思いをさせてしまった瞬間もあったと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To think about our journey so far‚\nthere were many difficult moments.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.6666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 109.8000037828
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "それでも変わらず私達を応援して、心から\n喜んでくれている。そんな人達の想いに応えたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ they continue to cheer for us and are truly\nhappy for us. I want to respond their feelings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "だから、これからもどんどん\nお仕事を受けさせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why‚ from now on‚ please let us\nhave more and more jobs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7160140052,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5917.3232063999985,
          "startTime": 126.6333372116
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 122.8666704494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。だけど、無理はしないようにな？\n……ん？　電話だ、ちょっとすまない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. But‚ don't push yourself too hard‚ okay?\n…Hmm? It's a phone call. Excuse me a moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はい、はい、なるほど……了解しました\n一度検討いたしますね。はい、それでは失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes‚ I see… I understand.\nI'll look into it. Yes‚ thank you for calling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.0000089645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 141.100008869
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "新しいお仕事の話ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was that about a new job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.100008869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。月ストへの依頼だったんだが……\n今日は時間も時間だし、明日にするか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. It was a request for Moon Tempest…\nIt's getting late today‚ I'll tell you tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.3000038783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 150.7333422023
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事をどんどん受けさせて下さい……って\nさっき言いましたよね。話だけでも聞かせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please let us have more and more jobs… That's\nWhat I just said a little while ago. At least let me hear about it now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.9000038783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "やる気満々だな。分かった。そろそろ撤収しないと\nいけないから、事務所で話そうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're really motivated. I got it. We have to get going soon‚ so\nlet's talk about it at the office‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.3666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 167.6165372116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今度、地方で開かれる音楽フェスがあるんだが\n月ストに出演依頼がきてるんだ。資料を見てくれるか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a music festival being held in the countryside this time‚\nand Moon Tempest got an offer to perform. Take a look at the materials.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.9247798696,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4641.890675300005,
          "startTime": 176.5666705449
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "音楽フェスですか。今回が第一回なんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A music festival… This is the first time it's being held.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.3333422023,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7389.995009300009,
          "startTime": 183.7233372116
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "現時点での出演者一覧を見ると分かると思うけど\nかなり気合いが入ったイベントになりそうなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you can tell from looking at the current lineup‚\nthat it's going to be a pretty ambitious event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.9000038783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "有名な歌手やアイドルが沢山……\n確かに凄いです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are a lot of famous singers and idols…\nIt's really amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.3784691486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "主催者の方は「ぜひ月ストにヘッドライナーを」と\nおっしゃってるんだが……スケジュールがネックでな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The organizers are insisting on having Moon Tempest\nas the headliner‚ but the schedule is a bit tight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.0333372116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "あ……なるほど。確かこのフェスの次の日は\n新曲のMV撮影がありましたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I see. Come to think of it‚ we have a music video shoot\nfor our new song the day after this festival‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.8333372116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ。イベントに出演するとなると\n移動時間も相まって負荷が高い。どうする？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. If we perform at the event‚\nthe travel time will also make it quite strenuous. What do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.2666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "ぜひ出演させて下さい\n今は少しでも沢山の人の前で歌いたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please let us perform.\nRight now‚ I want to sing in front of as many people as possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.9666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。渚達にも聞いてみるよ。それにしても……\n最近の琴乃は本当に元気一杯だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it. I'll ask Nagisa and the others too. Even so…\nYou've been really energetic lately‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.3666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。私自身、力がみなぎってる\n感じがするんです。あ、でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much. I feel like I'm overflowing\nwith power. Ah‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.9000038783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "忙しいのはありがたいんですけど……お姉ちゃんの\nお墓参りが出来てないのがちょっと気掛かりなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's great to be busy‚ but… I'm a little worried\nthat I haven't had a chance to visit my sister's grave.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.2000038783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……このスケジュールでは星見市に帰る余裕も\nあまりないよな。分かった、調整してみるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it… With this schedule‚ there's not much time\nto return to Hoshimi City. okay‚ I'll try to work something out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 256.1333372116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nお姉ちゃんには、報告したいことが沢山ありますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\nThere's so much I want to tell my sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.3333372116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――音楽フェス前日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day before the music festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.3666755357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-evening",
      "startTime": 269.5666755357
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-evening",
      "startTime": 269.5666755357
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn022.m4a",
      "text": "私だけ現地にいるっていうのも、なんだか不思議な\n感じがしますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being alone here at the venue… it makes me feel\nkind of strange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.3666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "フェスを紹介する生放送特番のナビゲーターに\nまさか琴乃が指名されるとはな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't expect you'd be the navigator\nfor a live special program introducing the festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 279.9000038783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-evening",
      "startTime": 282.7333645819
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn023.m4a",
      "text": "生放送はさすがに緊張しましたけど……スタッフや\n共演者のみなさんが優しくてなんとかなりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live broadcast was nerve-wracking‚ as expected… But the staff\nand other performers were kind‚ so I somehow managed to get through it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 287.3666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "うまくいって良かったよ\nさて、少し休んだら明日の確認をするか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad it went well.\nWell then‚ shall we go over tomorrow’s schedule after a short break?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 294.2000038783,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5133.383083200044,
          "startTime": 299.3333869615
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-evening",
      "startTime": 299.1000089645
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、飲み物を買って来たぞ……ん？　琴乃のところに\n誰か……あの様子だと、ファンみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ I got you something to drink… Hm? There's someone with Kotono…\nJudging by the situation‚ it seems like a fan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 305.8666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-evening",
      "startTime": 310.2333869615
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn024.m4a",
      "text": "フェスも来てくれるんですか！\n応援ありがとうございます、楽しみにしてて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're coming to the festival too?\nThank you for cheering‚ please look forward to it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 312.8666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-evening",
      "startTime": 317.7000536281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn025.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん\n飲み物、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san.\nThank you for the drink.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 320.0666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。最近、今まで以上に\nファンに声を掛けられる機会が増えたよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. Lately‚ more fans\nhave been approaching you than before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 325.5333372116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-evening",
      "startTime": 328.6000536281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn026.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。実は、さっきの子の前にも\n二回話し掛けられたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right. Actually‚ even before that girl‚\ntwo other people talked to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 333.4333372116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn027.m4a",
      "text": "話し掛けてもらえるのは嬉しいんですけど……\nもう少し堂々と対応したいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm happy to have people talk to me‚ but…\nI want to handle it more confidently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 339.7000038783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-evening",
      "startTime": 343.5000536281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃はそういうシャイなところも人気なんじゃないか？\nあまり堂々と対応しても相手に驚かれそうだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't your shyness part of what makes you so popular‚ Kotono?\nI think if you were too confident‚ you'd just surprise people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 347.1666705449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-evening",
      "startTime": 351.3000536281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn028.m4a",
      "text": "もう……{user}さんは\n私をなんだと思ってるんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seriously… {user}-san‚\nwhat do you think of me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 353.4283625148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん、それじゃあ\n明日のスケジュールを詰めようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ sorry. Well then‚\nShall we go over tomorrow's schedule?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 358.9000038783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "festout-00-evening",
      "startTime": 362.9666878382
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
